ich are functions\nonly of $p_c$ and $q_c$ of the respective lattice, to excellent general\napproximations of the multilayer connectivity threshold $q_c(M)$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 27 Feb 2014 20:30:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 7 Oct 2015 02:36:38 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 30 Dec 2015 12:22:13 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Fri, 27 May 2016 16:09:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-06-15"}
