a severe\nsystematic for cosmology in Stage-IV lensing surveys. We present useful scaling\nrelations to self-calibrate the SLC effect.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 28 Feb 2014 06:19:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 14 Apr 2015 05:56:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-04-15"}
